item.title: CVE-2024-8075|2024-08-22T19:31:05.823Z -- totolink -- ac1200%20t8
item.description: A vulnerability has been found in TOTOLINK AC1200 T8 4.1.5cu.862_B20230228 and classified as critical. Affected by this vulnerability is the function setDiagnosisCfg. The manipulation leads to os command injection. The attack can be launched remotely. NOTE: The vendor was contacted early about this disclosure but did not respond in any way.
